Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.29,0:22:25.23,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,你嘟着嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.23,0:22:31.41,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,表情里看出了小九九
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.18,0:22:36.26,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,因为那份若即若离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.26,0:22:46.17,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,被你藏到了口袋里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.17,0:22:53.10,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,回忆是黑白照片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.22,0:22:58.35,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,为它添上颜色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.83,0:23:06.90,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,再一次来到我的身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.90,0:23:12.07,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,我五彩斑斓的宝贝女儿
